{"word":"G4020 - περιεργάζομαι - periergázomai - per-ee-er-gad'-zom-ahee - Be a busybody","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιεργάζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>periergázomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>per-ee-er-gad'-zom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be a busybody"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வீண் அலுவற்காரராயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to bustle about uselessly, to busy oneself about trifling, needless, useless matters"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2038 - ἐργάζομαι - ergázomai - er-gad'-zom-ahee/2038\">G2038</a>; to <i>work</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>bustle about</i> (<i>meddle</i>): - be a busybody."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}